plot(cars)

data <- read.csv(file = "SM01_Aesthetic_Task.csv")
print(data)
sbj <- split (data, data$subj)
sbj[[1]]
library("retimes")
Reaction Time Analysis (version 0.1-2)
d = NULL
for (i in 1:100){
  dist <-  timefit(sbj[[i]]$durs)@par
  mu[i] <- dist[1]
  sig[i] <- dist[2]
  tau[i] <- dist[3]
}
d <- rbind(d, data.frame(mu, sig, tau))
d$subject <- 1:nrow(d)
print(d)
for (x in 1:100){
  durs_mean [x] <- mean(sbj[[x]]$durs)
}
print(durs_mean)

mem_data <- read.csv(file = "SM01_Memorize_Task.csv")
print(mem_data)
mem_sbj <- split (mem_data, mem_data$subj)
mem_sbj[[1]]
df = NULL
for (i in 1:100){
  dist <-  timefit(mem_sbj[[i]]$durs)@par
  mu[i] <- dist[1]
  sig[i] <- dist[2]
  tau[i] <- dist[3]
}
df <- rbind(df, data.frame(mu, sig, tau))
df$subject <- 1:nrow(df)
print(df)
write.csv(df, file = "Memorize_Gauss.csv", row.names=FALSE)
